name: Weseler straße
text: This is a busy street!! A car passed by when the air quality was measured by the bike and gave off a lot of particles!! But the LANUV station and the sensebox show the air quality is fine.

name: Umgehungsstraße
text: The area around you has a lot of trees and less traffic. The air quality here is much better than the place before.

name: LANUV-Geist
text: The LANUV station in Geist is here. It is surrounded by trees as well.
